l/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d73c371df144e7693330f27efcd646a4f9d19c8","tid":474151,"uid":48680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一個人黎到呢個世界，都係一個人離開，<br />\n中間何必有太多與人交接</blockquote><br />\n其實唔使<br />\n亦都冇人可以比個說服到你既講法<br />\n<br />\n但我會話 <br />\n中間有多d 有意義 既相遇<br />\n我覺得唔錯 <br />\n<br />\n如果你真係撫心自問<br />\n冇人陪你好過有 <br />\n咁就開開心心接受啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ca4d822938921cf1156ab74eb20b83977290b7","tid":474151,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:01:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}